3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the transmission of sequences of symbols, which is a fundamental problem in multimedia communication. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with the capacity analysis of a communication channel, which is a topic of interest in networking and internet architecture. 
5. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper uses convex geometry to analyze the capacity of the communication channel, which involves computational complexity.
